      <title>美国核心个人消费支出指数 (PCE) 表现疲弱，12 月消费者支出稳健</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-31/us-core-pce-muted-consumer-spending-solid-in-dec-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储最看重的美国通胀指标，即所谓的核心个人消费支出价格指数，较 11 月小幅上涨 0.2%，而 12 月家庭支出上涨 0.7%。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台对这些数据进行了分析。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-31/us-core-pce-muted-consumer-spending-solid-in-dec-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:01:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>被动投资时代驳斥“神奇”有效市场理论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/-magical-efficient-market-theory-rebuked-in-era-of-big-passive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乍一看，本周的股市交易很难成为市场效率理论的典范，这一理论是经济学入门课中经常被浪漫化的概念。毕竟，受一周前发布的人工智能模型引发的担忧推动，大型股指周一暴跌，随后迅速反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/-magical-efficient-market-theory-rebuked-in-era-of-big-passive</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:00:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鲍曼希望在降息前进一步推动通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/fed-s-bowman-wants-more-inflation-progress-before-cutting-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事米歇尔鲍曼表示，她希望看到通胀在央行进一步降低利率之前取得更多进展，并质疑在经济强劲的情况下如何实施限制性政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/fed-s-bowman-wants-more-inflation-progress-before-cutting-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国商业银行首席执行官在与奥塞尔对决时公布新薪酬</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/commerzbank-announces-400-million-share-buyback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国商业银行首席执行官 Bettina Orlopp 宣布了一项新一轮的股票回购计划，并承诺将继续增加派息，以保护该银行免受意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 的潜在收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/commerzbank-announces-400-million-share-buyback</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 12:51:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
